      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "TTRPG Tools - Time 0.5.0\r\n\r\nNew:\r\n- Frontmatter import and export. You can now set up import and export for your events created with frontmatter.\r\n- Event explorer. Search your events for quick access.\r\n- Apply weather to date ranges. You can now quickly apply regional weather to your calendar without creating events.\r\n- New setting Fahrenheit or Celsius.\r\n- Buttons for manage frontmatter(hammer icon), scan active note frontmatter(scan icon, try this first), scan whole vault frontmatter(search on folder icon), apply weather pack to date ranges(drizzle cloud icon), event explorer (search icon)\r\n\r\nChanged:\r\n- Increased max. moon size in the day view from 96 to 300.\r\n- Recurrence events index is now stored in the recurrence.index.json to prevent creating to many json files as year.index.json\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/Jareika/ttrpg-tools-time/compare/0.4.1...0.5.0\r\n\r\n<img width=\"920\" height=\"883\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/a0c6e04f-5eb0-42d7-bafd-818b01352cd0\" />\r\n\r\n<img width=\"326\" height=\"400\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/5369c69a-dfbe-4911-b4d8-f61a35fd9f0c\" />\r\n\r\n<img width=\"910\" height=\"277\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/246185cd-5c5f-430a-8a91-55d66f0b9d13\" />\r\n\r\n<img width=\"136\" height=\"76\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/db7d7c53-e0d5-4759-b5fb-fb5d95b7b6c1\" />\r\n\r\n<img width=\"280\" height=\"274\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/2b29b923-0bb9-4e77-bdf1-3c47a678ae69\" />\r\n",
