      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "Improved loading time for the calendar view especially for later years like 100.000.\r\nDelete event from timeline or day view.\r\n\r\nBetter arranged settings:\r\n<img width=\"631\" height=\"745\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/c8362278-62f3-41a3-a7ec-f9936d999c72\" />\r\n\r\nSlimmer Edit calendar:\r\n<img width=\"593\" height=\"472\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/511c0e42-d4e0-4534-82fc-f7cedff86268\" />\r\n\r\nLeap days append to month option.\r\n\r\nWeekday flow into months:\r\n\r\n<img width=\"677\" height=\"65\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/d2bb91a7-5aac-4a0c-946b-c48e46706393\" />\r\n\r\nEras with more options to let a era end without starting a new one:\r\n\r\n<img width=\"835\" height=\"243\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/d559b68b-5322-4709-a75b-5b47d68c74d9\" />\r\n\r\nAnd these two little things:\r\n\r\n<img width=\"283\" height=\"48\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/93e1c7dd-aaf8-4ee4-bbcd-195d4a770c06\" />\r\n\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/Jareika/ttrpg-tools-time/compare/0.3.3...0.4.0",
