      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "New:\r\n- Timeline view\r\n  - Open the timeline view and display your calendar events as timeline.\r\n    - Open the Timeline filters (side pane window) and select wich Events you want to see in your timeline. No active filter it shows all. One active filter it only shows the events with this tag, exclude with douple click on a filter to cross filter.\r\n- Time controls a side pane window to control your time. You find there buttons to control the timeline and when you have set it up buttons to let the time pass.\r\n  - The time pass buttons must be added by yourself in the plugin settings.\r\n    - Give them a label and or an icon and set hours or minutes.\r\n- Insert timeline: You can use the insert timeline command or button from control view to insert a timeline in your notes as YAML. This is needed to publish them. I have to make the publish part also in the TTRPG Tools - Publish but this later.\r\n\r\n<img width=\"570\" height=\"299\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/1b4cc778-1884-4575-b822-573c5ac6eefa\" />\r\n<img width=\"583\" height=\"678\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/70bb4a6f-6699-40c3-8193-16944cdd7228\" />\r\n<img width=\"1560\" height=\"1704\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/efede699-df36-4727-81ae-cbb5d9c07e0b\" />\r\n<img width=\"813\" height=\"1176\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/39178db3-9093-4a86-9b42-a1f711c99ee5\" />\r\n\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/Jareika/ttrpg-tools-time/compare/0.2.7...0.3.0",
